Package: pdftextclusteR
Title: Properly importing text from PDF files that may contain columns or other text boxes
Version: 0.0.0.9002
Authors@R: 
    person("Coen", "Eisma", , "coeneisma@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0007-9001-2572"))
Description: For importing PDF files, the pdftools package is available. 
    However, this package does not work optimally when dealing with PDF files 
    containing multiple columns. The pdftextclusteR package uses a 
    Density-Based Spatial Clustering algorithm to determine which words are 
    (likely) associated with each other.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://coeneisma.github.io/pdftextclusteR/
